scenes.description: Polka and Zeta talk about the items they got and take a celebratory photo for Zeta's 3D debut.
Zeta is left alone after Polka steals the "Zeta Min" jar. She decides to use her key to proceed to the next area.
Zeta enters a Jazz Club themed room, explores the instruments, and finds a cat in the audience.
Zeta plays a short piece on the piano.
Zeta finishes playing the piano and decides to sing a song in the Jazz Club.
